{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Base directory for this skill: /Users/griogrii_riabov/.claude/plugins/cache/aidd-local/feature-dev-aidd/0.1.0/skills/status\n\nFollow `feature-dev-aidd:aidd-core` and `feature-dev-aidd:aidd-loop`.\n\n## Steps\n1. Run `python3 /Users/griogrii_riabov/.claude/plugins/cache/aidd-local/feature-dev-aidd/0.1.0/skills/status/runtime/status.py --ticket <ticket>` for the canonical stage entrypoint.\n2. If index data is missing or stale, run `python3 /Users/griogrii_riabov/.claude/plugins/cache/aidd-local/feature-dev-aidd/0.1.0/skills/status/runtime/index_sync.py --ticket <ticket>`.\n3. Return the output contract and the status summary.\n\n## Command contracts\n### `python3 /Users/griogrii_riabov/.claude/plugins/cache/aidd-local/feature-dev-aidd/0.1.0/skills/status/runtime/status.py`\n- When to run: canonical status command for read-only ticket summary.\n- Inputs: optional `--ticket <ticket>` (falls back to active ticket when available).\n- Outputs: consolidated stage/status snapshot and artifact pointers.\n- Failure mode: non-zero exit when ticket resolution or index/report reads fail.\n- Next action: refresh index or fix missing ticket context, then rerun status runtime.\n\n## Notes\n- Loop stage: set `AIDD:ACTIONS_LOG` to the most recent `*.actions.json` under `aidd/reports/actions/<ticket>/...` (use `rg` if needed).\n\n## Additional resources\n- Runtime implementation: [runtime/status.py](runtime/status.py) (when: status aggregation behavior needs debugging; why: verify ticket resolution and output fields).\n\n\nARGUMENTS: TST-001"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"28cefa57-de91-45f4-bdfe-02fc2843f5ab","uuid":"1a43165f-59d7-4268-8763-946919688bf4","isSynthetic":true}
