est --tests \"*RoleEventsController*\"`\n   398→    - `./gradlew :backend-mcp:test --tests \"*RoleEventService*\"`\n   399→  - Exit criteria:\n   400→    - SSE endpoint returns event stream\n   401→    - Role changes trigger notifications\n   402→    - Subscribers receive updates within 5 seconds\n   403→    - Proper cleanup on disconnect\n   404→  - Steps:\n   405→    - Create RoleEventService with Sinks.Many\n   406→    - Create RoleEventsController with SSE producer\n   407→    - Create RoleAssignmentService\n   408→    - Integrate notification on role change\n   409→    - Add heartbeat flux\n   410→    - Write integration tests for SSE\n   411→    - Write tests for role assignment notifications\n   412→  - Tests:\n   413→    - profile: targeted\n   414→    - tasks: `./gradlew :backend-mcp:test --tests \"*RoleEvent*\"`\n   415→    - filters: `RoleEventsControllerTest`, `RoleEventServiceTest`\n   416→  - Acceptance mapping: AC-3, AC-2\n   417→  - Risks & mitigations:\n   418→    - Memory leak from subscriptions → Cleanup on cancel/terminate\n   419→    - Too many concurrent connections → Subscriber limits\n   420→  - Dependencies: I4\n   421→\n   422→---\n   423→\n   424→## AIDD:NEXT_3\n   425→> 3 ближайших implement‑чекбокса. Pointer list: 1–2 строки и `ref:` на детализацию.\n   426→- [ ] I3: Profile service integration + Role caching (ref: iteration_id=I3)\n   427→## AIDD:OUT_OF_SCOPE_BACKLOG\n   428→> Побочные идеи/задачи, которые НЕ входят в текущий work_item (без расширения scope).\n   429→- [ ] Redis distributed cache for roles (source: research)\n   430→- [ ] WebSocket alternative to SSE (source: spec)\n   431→- [ ] Admin UI for role management (source: prd)\n   432→- [ ] Audit log retention automation (source: plan)\n   433→\n   434→---\n   435→\n   436→## AIDD:HANDOFF_INBOX\n   437→> Сюда падают задачи из Research/Review/QA (с source: aidd/reports/...).\n   438→\n   439→\n   440→---\n   441→\n   442→<!-- handoff:manual start -->\n   443→<!-- handoff:manual end -->\n   444→## AIDD:QA_TRACEABILITY\n   445→> AC → check → result → evidence.\n   446→- AC-1 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n   447→- AC-2 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n   448→- AC-3 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n   449→- AC-4 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n   450→## AIDD:CHECKLIST\n   451→\n   452→### AIDD:CHECKLIST_SPEC\n   453→- [x] PRD: Status READY (и нет незакрытых blocker вопросов)\n   454→- [x] Research: Status reviewed\n   455→- [x] Plan: существует и валиден\n   456→- [x] Review Spec: Plan Review READY + PRD Review READY\n   457→- [ ] Spec interview (optional): spec обновлён; затем `/feature-dev-aidd:tasks-new` для синхронизации tasklist\n   458→\n   459→### AIDD:CHECKLIST_IMPLEMENT\n   460→- [x] Реализован функционал для checkbox #1 из AIDD:NEXT_3 (I2)\n   461→- [x] Добавлены/обновлены тесты по плану\n   462→- [x] Обновлён AIDD:CONTEXT_PACK (scope + test policy)\n   463→- [x] Обновлён AIDD:TEST_EXECUTION (если менялась тестовая тактика)\n   464→- [x] Прогресс отмечен (см. AIDD:PROGRESS_LOG)\n   465→\n   466→### AIDD:CHECKLIST_REVIEW\n   467→- [ ] Reviewer: замечания добавлены в tasklist (handoff)\n   468→- [ ] Требуемость тестов выставлена (если используете reviewer marker)\n   469→- [ ] Изменения соответствуют plan/PRD (нет лишнего)\n   470→\n   471→### AIDD:CHECKLIST_QA\n   472→- [ ] QA: AIDD:ACCEPTANCE проверены (traceability)\n   473→- [ ] QA report сохранён (aidd/reports/qa/TST-001.json)\n   474→- [ ] Known issues задокументированы\n   475→\n   476→---\n   477→\n   478→## AIDD:PROGRESS_LOG\n   479→> Мини‑лог: фиксируй кратко, обновляй после каждой итерации.\n   480→> Формат записи:\n   481→> `- YYYY-MM-DD source=implement id=I4 kind=iteration hash=abc123 link=aidd/reports/tests/<ticket>/TST-001.jsonl msg=short-note`\n   482→\n   483→- 2026-03-18 source=implement id=I1 kind=iteration hash=a1f45f2 link=aidd/reports/loops/TST-001/I1 msg=\"Database migration + RBAC domain model complete. 10 files created, tests pass.\"\n   484→- 20