{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_jGLLpuujRsIycuWFUb4RPRtf","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.aiadvent.mcp.backend.rbac.persistence;\n     2→\n     3→import java.time.Instant;\n     4→import java.util.UUID;\n     5→import org.springframework.data.domain.Page;\n     6→import org.springframework.data.domain.Pageable;\n     7→import org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\n     8→import org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\n     9→\n    10→/**\n    11→ * Spring Data JPA repository for {@link AuditLogEntity}.\n    12→ */\n    13→@Repository\n    14→public interface AuditLogRepository extends JpaRepository<AuditLogEntity, UUID> {\n    15→\n    16→    /**\n    17→     * Find audit log entries by actor namespace and reference.\n    18→     *\n    19→     * @param actorNamespace the actor's namespace\n    20→     * @param actorReference the actor's reference\n    21→     * @param pageable       pagination information\n    22→     * @return a page of audit log entries\n    23→     */\n    24→    Page<AuditLogEntity> findByActorNamespaceAndActorReference(\n    25→            String actorNamespace, String actorReference, Pageable pageable);\n    26→\n    27→    /**\n    28→     * Find audit log entries within a timestamp range.\n    29→     *\n    30→     * @param start    the start timestamp (inclusive)\n    31→     * @param end      the end timestamp (inclusive)\n    32→     * @param pageable pagination information\n    33→     * @return a page of audit log entries\n    34→     */\n    35→    Page<AuditLogEntity> findByTimestampBetween(\n    36→            Instant start, Instant end, Pageable pageable);\n    37→}\n    38→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_pNtJ92ksp9R4YhIJwRvx4R98","session_id":"28cefa57-de91-45f4-bdfe-02fc2843f5ab","uuid":"3c889010-6bbf-4e4c-ae65-044802eb22eb"}
